Model 1 : Log of income explained by the level of education

fm1 <- lm(loginc ~ educ, df)
summary(fm1)

Diagnostics plots

plot(fm1)

Fitted values

df$y1 <- fitted(fm1)

Graphics of predictor vs fitted values

p1 <- ggplot(df, aes(x=educ, y=y1))
p1 + geom_point()
